"Commercial Purpose" means any use that is primarily intended for or directed
toward commercial advantage or monetary compensation, including (without
limitation):
(a) use in connection with providing services to others;
(b) use in a product or service that is sold, licensed, or otherwise monetized;
(c) use to support or operate the business activities of an Organization; and
(d) use to generate revenue, fees, advertising income, or other economic
